Lime Testing Framework
======================

Lime is a usable testing framework for PHP 5 created by Bernhard Schussek
and Fabien Potencier. See the documentation in the `doc/` directory or on the 
[GitHub wiki] [1] for more information about how to use Lime.

The library is released under the MIT license. See the attached LICENSE
file for the license text.

    [1] http://wiki.github.com/bschussek/lime